_sText: This is my best work I ever made. I spent nearly a year to create it. There are 10 maps including some maps I early made like mg_run4life, awp_unlimited and cs_area_823 changed to a pacman game. I put a map inspired from the flash game called Cubefield, an XC map, a map inspired from mg_precision, another inspired from mg_impactgun, a red light green light map, a map inspired from mg_musicalrooms and an experimental map. Have fun! :) NEW VERSION: mg_multimap_orbital_fix4
